Created the Node.js/Express FAQ app with SQLite storage.

Files added:
- `package.json`
- `server.js`
- `views/public.ejs`
- `views/login.ejs`
- `views/editor.ejs`
- `public/styles.css`
- `README.md`

The app runs on port `5041` by default, creates `faq.sqlite` automatically, includes public keyword filtering grouped by category, and has a logged-in editor flow for adding, editing, deleting, and ordering categories and FAQ entries.

Per the provided working agreement, I did not install dependencies, run the app, or execute tests.
diff --git a/README.md b/README.md
