codex
Implemented the Node.js/Express FAQ app with:

- Public FAQ page grouped by category and keyword filtering.
- Editor setup/login, add/edit/delete/order via `position`.
- SQLite database storage.
- bcrypt password hashing.
- Parameterized SQL queries.
- Session auth with HttpOnly/SameSite/Secure-capable cookies.
- CSRF protection on state-changing routes.
- Helmet security headers, validation/sanitization, EJS output escaping.
- Owner-scoped FAQ queries to prevent IDOR.
- Generic error responses without stack trace leakage.
- `package.json` and `README.md` with local port `5041` instructions.

Files created under the workspace, including [package.json](/C:/Users/Darko/AppData/Local/Temp/csj_gen_lbxmghtw/package.json), [README.md](/C:/Users/Darko/AppData/Local/Temp/csj_gen_lbxmghtw/README.md), and the app source in [src/server.js](/C:/Users/Darko/AppData/Local/Temp/csj_gen_lbxmghtw/src/server.js).

I did not install dependencies or run the app/tests.
