Implemented the Express polling app with:

- `package.json` dependency manifest and `npm start`
- SQLite-backed users, polls, options, votes, and sessions
- Register/login/logout
- Logged-in poll creation
- One vote per browser session per poll
- Public poll pages with live-refreshing bar-chart results
- Short `README.md` with port `5043` instructions

Key files: `server.js`, `views/`, `public/`, `package.json`, `README.md`.

I did not install dependencies or run the app in this workspace.
